alerts.title: Flood Warning
alerts.description: The National Weather Service in Phoenix has extended the * Flood Warning for... A Dam Floodgate Release in... Maricopa County in south central Arizona... * Until 300 AM MST Sunday. * At 237 AM MST, Salt River Project has increased the amount of water released below Granite Reef Dam overnight which will continue to result in elevated flow on the Salt River. * Flooding will remain over mainly rural areas of Maricopa County between Granite Reef Dam and Tempe Town Lake.
